py3tuio is a very basic, crude and compact implementation of a TUIO 1.x server written in Python 3 using pyliblo. It is currently restricted to a 2D interactive surface and does not distinguish between different clients.

- Armin, March 6th, 2012


Requirements
============
liblo Ã­s a lightweight OSC implementation
pyliblo is a Python wrapper for liblo and available here: http://das.nasophon.de/pyliblo/

Basic use (demo)
================
python3 py3tuio.py

